latestIgtvVideos.caption:
#StyleSprucing Episode 20
#SpruceYourStylewithPara
Colour-Blocking 101:
You are literally missing out on so much fun and a vibrant way to express your style personality, if you haven’t tried colour blocking, yet. Colour blocking involves using “blocks of colour” in your outfit to create a bold, eye-catching look.
The look can be very effective and flattering on anyone, if done correctly!Here, I am showing you how I color block. There will more tips I will be sharing on my feed posts for the same🤓🤓🤓
.

latestIgtvVideos.title: À La Mode Style Edit!
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
#StyleSprucing Episode 15
#SpruceYourStylewithPara
À La Mode by @shristichetani.kolkata X Paranosh Irani. Let me know which look is your favourite 1,2,3 or 4👇🏻👇🏻
::Details::
Look 1 and 2 consists of ‘The Emerald Green Top’ encrusted with green bead work and it is such a versatile piece of garment that you can pair it with literally anything. Monotone looks are a current trend and I am giving you’ll two completely different options. In Look 1, I am keeping it classy with the flared green pants from @zaraindiaofficial with neutral earthy accessories and in Look 2, I add a bit of sassy and quirk with the green faux leather skirt from @primark with snake print accessories and that retro white pair of sunnies!
Look 3 and 4 consists of the flamboyant black cape with grey and black encrusted bead work. In Look 3, I have kept it boho chique, with the boho accessories and high heels. In Look 4, I used the cape and kept the monotone look in mind with the flared black pants and singled while going heavy with the accessory details!
Hope you’ll enjoyed this video :)
.
Until next time keep Sprucing your Style!!
.
Music: Sia- Cheap Thrills (Ramp walk mix) EDM by Devilz
.
